dct_title_s: Map of the Upper Mississippi River : from the mouth of the Ohio River to Lake Itasca, Minn. in fifty sheets
dct_description_sm: Sheets numbered 101 to 150.; Sheets 101-146 drawn by C.W. Clark; sheet 147 drawn by C.W. Clark and H.A.H. d'Ailly; sheets 148-150 drawn by H.A.H. d'Ailly, title page drawn by Paul Burgoldt.; Sheets 101-103 reprinted in 1928.; Relief shown by hachures.; Indicates land ownership.
